### Get Auth Token
# @name login
POST {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/auth/email/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{TEST_EMAIL}}",
  "password": "{{TEST_PASSWORD}}"
}

### Set token variable from login response
@token = {{login.token}}

### ===========================================
### DELETE COST CENTERS ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Delete Cost Center by ID (Soft Delete)
DELETE {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===========================================
### BULK DELETE COST CENTERS ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Bulk Delete Cost Centers (Multiple IDs)
DELETE {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/bulk-delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "ids": [10, 11, 12, 13, 14]
}
